<D>__{i really think you're}
<C>__{schaefer}
<D>__{you wanna commit suicide, fine! you got some death wish, fine! but you will not drag this company down with you!}
<C>__{welles}
<D>__{it was a joke, george}
<A>__{schaefer slaps welles firmly across the face. welles is stunned.}
<C>__{schaefer}
<D>__{there are no jokes! there are people making a living. there is food on the table!}
<A>__{schaefer glares at him and then rages off welles straightens his suit and then, with a shaking hand, reaches for a cigar. he tries to laugh, but cannot.}
